Description: Functions for proficiency testing analysis including robust
    statistics (Algorithm A, nIQR, MADe), score calculations (z, z', zeta, En),
    and homogeneity/stability assessments per ISO 13528:2022 and ISO 17043:2024.
    Developed under contract OSE-282-3065-2025.
